'''走鹃'''（{{lang-en|'''Roadrunner'''}}），是一套由[[IBM|IBM]]為[[美國能源部|美國能源部]]（Department of Energy）所屬的{{tsl|en|National Nuclear Security Administration|國家核安全管理局}}（NNSA）建立的[[超級電腦|超級電腦]]，此電腦以[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]][[州鳥|州鳥]][[走鵑|走鵑]]（[[學名|學名]]：''{{lang|la|Geococcyx californianus}}''）命名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.cnyes.com/stock/dspnewsS.asp?fi=%5CNEWSBASE%5C20080611%5CWEB1319&vi=33819&date=20080611&time=13:47:31&pagetype=usastock&subtype=home&cls=usastock_totalnews|title=美國展示全球最快電腦 運算速度相當於10萬台NB|accessdate=2008-06-11|author=查淑妝|date=2008-06-11|publisher=[[鉅亨網|鉅亨網]]}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，設於新墨西哥州的[[洛斯阿拉莫斯国家实验室|洛斯阿拉莫斯国家实验室]]。在2008年5月25日時，此套電腦的運算能力已達到1.026[[FLOPS|PetaFLOPS]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.computerworld.com/action/article.do?command=viewArticleBasic&taxonomyName=hardware&articleId=9095318&taxonomyId=12&intsrc=kc_top|title=IBM's Roadrunner smashes 4-minute mile of supercomputing|accessdate=2008-06-10|author=Sharon Gaudin|date=2008-06-09|publisher=Computerworld|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081224001155/http://www.computerworld.com/action/article.do?command=viewArticleBasic&taxonomyName=hardware&articleId=9095318&taxonomyId=12&intsrc=kc_top|archivedate=2008-12-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url = http://news.cnet.com/Military-supercomputer-sets-record/2100-1010_3-6241145.html?tag=nefd.top |title = Military supercomputer sets record - CNET News.com |access-date = 2008-06-11 |archive-date = 2019-09-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190924200923/https://www.cnet.com/news/military-supercomputer-sets-record/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7443557.stm | publisher = BBC | title = Supercomputer sets petaflop pace | accessdate = 2008-06-09 | date = 2008-06-09 | archive-date = 2009-02-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090222034804/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/technology/7443557.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref> ，成為前500大超級電腦中第一個持續運算能力超過<1>[[每秒浮點運算次數|PetaFLOPS]](10<sup>15</sup>/s)者。耗资1.33亿美元<ref>{{cite news | author=JOHN MARKOFF | last= | coauthors= | title=Military Supercomputer Sets Record | date=June 9, 2008 | publisher= | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/09/technology/09petaflops.html?_r=1&oref=slogin | work=The New York Times | pages= | accessdate=2008-06-11 | language= | archive-date=2020-11-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109043042/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/09/technology/09petaflops.html?_r=1&oref=slogin | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 架構 ==
=== 硬體 ===
'''Roadrunner'''採用混合式架構，並以'''「TriBlades」'''，即一片裝有2顆[[Opteron|Opteron]]雙核心CPU及8GB[[記憶體|記憶體]]的LS21型[[刀鋒伺服器|刀鋒伺服器]]和2片各有兩顆PowerXCell 8i處理器、各8GB RAM的QS22型刀鋒伺服器插在一片有4條[[PCI-Express|PCI-Express]] 8x的擴充卡板所組成。每片TriBlades間以[[Infiniband|Infiniband]]相互連結。3套TriBlades放入一組BladeCenter H機箱中，一個機櫃可容納四組BladeCenter H機箱，一共用了296個[[機櫃|機櫃]]，共有6,912顆[[AMD|AMD]] [[Opteron|Opteron]]雙核心[[CPU|CPU]]以及12,960顆[[Cell|PowerXCell 8i處理器]]，記憶體加起來有103.6[[Terabyte|TB]]<ref name="OVERVIEW">{{cite web|url=http://www.lanl.gov/orgs/hpc/roadrunner/pdfs/Koch%20-%20Roadrunner%20Overview/RR%20Seminar%20-%20System%20Overview.pdf|publisher=Los Alamos National Laboratory|title=RR Seminar - System Overview|accessdate=2008-05-31|date=2008-03-13|archive-date=2012-03-14|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/669Wtg1kU?url=http://www.lanl.gov/orgs/hpc/roadrunner/pdfs/Koch%20-%20Roadrunner%20Overview/RR%20Seminar%20-%20System%20Overview.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>
。
== 意義 ==
所謂「千兆級浮點運算」（petaflop）意指運算速度可達每秒千兆次。超級電腦運算技術也被視為國家經濟競爭力的象徵。

=== 軟體 ===
Roadrunner的[[作業系統|作業系統]]使用[[Red_Hat_Enterprise_Linux|Red Hat Enterprise Linux]]，使用[[Open_MPI|Open MPI]][[訊息傳遞介面|訊息傳遞介面]]函式庫 <ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.open-mpi.org/papers/sc-2008/jsquyres-cisco-booth-talk-1up.pdf| format=PDF| author=Jeff Squyres| publisher=[[Open_MPI|Open MPI]]| title=Open MPI: 10^15 Flops Can't Be Wrong| accessdate=2008-11-22| archive-date=2021-02-23| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223014051/https://www.open-mpi.org/papers/sc-2008/jsquyres-cisco-booth-talk-1up.pdf| dead-url=no}}</ref> ，並裝有[[xCAT|xCAT]][[分散式運算|分散式運算]]軟體。

== 用途 ==
Roadrunner主要供美國能源部計算美國核能武器儲存量的安全及可靠性<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ithome.com.tw/itadm/article.php?c=49313 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-06-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080614134025/http://www.ithome.com.tw/itadm/article.php?c=49313 |archivedate=2008-06-14 }}</ref>
。另外亦可提供[[科學|科學]]、[[金融|金融]]、[[汽車|汽車]]及[[航天|航空工業]]等領域的運算。

==退役==
2013年3月，洛薩拉摩斯國家實驗室宣佈Roadrunner退役，并将于3月31日关闭。<ref name=Ars1>{{cite web | url=http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/03/worlds-fastest-supercomputer-from-09-is-now-obsolete-will-be-dismantled/ | title=World’s top supercomputer from ‘09 is now obsolete, will be dismantled | publisher=Ars Technica | accessdate=March 31, 2013 | first=Jon | last=Brodkin | archive-date=2013-03-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130331203506/http://arstechnica.com/information-technology/2013/03/worlds-fastest-supercomputer-from-09-is-now-obsolete-will-be-dismantled/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>雖然其運算能力排在第22名，效能仍佳，但因耗電量太大（達成1Peta FLOPS運算量需耗2345千瓦電），不符現今節能運算的趨勢而退出現役超級電腦之林<ref>{{cite news|url=http://mag.udn.com/mag/vote2007-08/storypage.jsp?f_ART_ID=448530|title=因耗電過大 IBM超級電腦「Roadrunner」退役|publisher=聯合新聞網|date=2013-04-01}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

